{"tid":2384202,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"林建岳同古天樂開新公司Cool Style拍港產片 Angelababy任策略性股東","createTime":"2021-01-28T11:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T12:00:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9eab3af858ab66e39660a16229e6a67fa56062aa","tid":2384202,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:50:00.000Z","msg":"林建岳旗下寰亞傳媒集團有限公司（寰亞傳媒），今日宣佈將與古天樂旗下的天下一集團有限公司，成立新公司Cool Style，以及由Kim Chou創辦的風尚國際（Style International），將會共同營運及拓展新娛樂事業板塊。而新公司將會提供藝人管理、製作本地電影、以及拓展社交媒體的短視頻等業務外，更會為業界培育新演員，而馮德倫創辦的製作公司FMP，將會參與短片的創作及製作，至於Angelababy（楊穎）則成為新公司的策略性股東。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210128/NGAJIQVMSFAIZPP5UM5Q7XRDNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210128%2FNGAJIQVMSFAIZPP5UM5Q7XRDNA%2F&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=819cec64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210128%2FNGAJIQVMSFAIZPP5UM5Q7XRDNA%2F&h=c6d70d90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210128/NGAJIQVMSFAIZPP5UM5Q7XRDNA/</a>"},{"pid":"eb4684a38c559daf77e68cabb06c24c5a7f94b6f","tid":2384202,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"成班唔識做戲既人培養新人同拍戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港先做得出"},{"pid":"650e1f3d41691f990a5909a16b303e41c952c986","tid":2384202,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"一定唔會睇"}]}